# Specs Directory

This directory will contain feature specifications organized by feature name.

Each feature will have its own subdirectory with:
- spec.md: Feature specification
- plan.md: Technical implementation plan
- tasks.md: Task breakdown

Example structure:
```
specs/
├── jwt-authentication/
│   ├── spec.md
│   ├── plan.md
│   └── tasks.md
└── account-transfers/
    ├── spec.md
    ├── plan.md
    └── tasks.md
```
